OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fin the evening with bright then clear
OL,7,Fspells and variable cloud. Mostly dry
OL,8,Fovernight but turning cloudier. Small
OL,9,Fchance of the odd light shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FDry with variable cloud and
OL,12,Fbright spells through the morning.
OL,13,FSome rain spreads east through the
OL,14,Fafternoon, perhaps heavy at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,17,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,18,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,19,Fdrier and brighter periods too,
OL,20,Fespecially in the east.
